實咪有唔同程度嘅壓力<br />\n<br />\n另外sw你讀完個asso就諗住做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你就讀完degree基本上都係機構入面最底層個個<br />\n你諗吓你自己壓力大唔大啦"},{"pid":"d622b9937d106b730c6cbe52e89ccbf568b66de7","tid":1398050,"uid":228436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca65af23e637448b2e4aecde7ebf7b803123d66e","tid":1398050,"uid":234025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:19:37.000Z","msg":"想知東華en 係咪好差？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:14:17.000Z","msg":"點解你會覺得差先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為東華呢個名定係針對課程本身先？<br />\n名呢樣嘢我就解決唔到嘅<br />\n但係你諗吓其實呢個課程係拎到en牌<br />\n咁護士牌呢樣嘢係咪真係咁容易拎呢<br />\n求求其其就可以比人？"},{"pid":"8d9e9dd0111f0661b62c7165037dc96875af7ff4","tid":1398050,"uid":153592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:16:59.000Z","msg":"Nursing 無後悔"},{"pid":"0e6865f52d92e5e02d1977590ec2ff57b1a431e7","tid":1398050,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d622b9937d106b730c6cbe52e89ccbf568b66de7","tid":1398050,"uid":228436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca65af23e637448b2e4aecde7ebf7b803123d66e","tid":1398050,"uid":234025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:19:37.000Z","msg":"想知東華en 係咪好差？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:14:17.000Z","msg":"點解你會覺得差先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為東華呢個名定係針對課程本身先？<br />\n名呢樣嘢我就解決唔到嘅<br />\n但係你諗吓其實呢個課程係拎到en牌<br />\n咁護士牌呢樣嘢係咪真係咁容易拎呢<br />\n求求其其就可以比人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T20:22:46.000Z","msg":"事實係易拎，比得起錢基本上guarantee有牌<br />\n考試tips多，合格唔難，clinical既tutor鬆手<br />\n我眼見好多冇腦student都即將會pass<br />\n只不過真係做唔掂既話，到時同事針你杯你就另一回事<br />\n<br />\n講番櫻主問題，其實要諗既話代表nursing唔啱你<br />\n社工都可以揸下攤，但護士既環境係冇心做真係好痛苦"}]}